  <name>Pandabox</name>
  <summary>Secure password manager with encryption</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      Pandabox is a secure, open-source password manager built with Rust, offering robust encryption and a user-friendly interface.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Secure password storage using industry-standard encryption</li>
      <li>Master password protection with Argon2 key derivation</li>
      <li>Modern, responsive UI</li>
      <li>Secure password generation</li>
      <li>Import/Export functionality</li>
      <li>Cross-platform compatibility</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
